116 A.3d 473 In the Matter of the REINSTATEMENT OF Joel D. JOSEPH to the Practice of Law. Misc. Docket AG No. 11,

Sept. Term, 2015.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. June 17, 2015.

ORDER

This matter came before the Court on the Petition for Reinstatement of Joel D. Joseph, the supplement to the petition and the Response of Bar Counsel; and

The Court having considered the Petition, the supplement and Response, it is this 17th day of June, 2015, by the Court of Appeals of Maryland;

ORDERED, that the Petition and supplement be, and the same are hereby DENIED.
